{"tid":788511,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【一買即坐艇】龍蟠苑買家樓都未收 層樓已跌價10%","createTime":"2018-08-21T13:59:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T14:26:39.000Z","uid":22839,"like":149,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"dde9a7719062a2fa150b94b2a9d1a0f91ce26c5d","tid":788511,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T13:59:28.000Z","msg":"二手樓爆劈價潮，居屋更出現「一買即坐艇」慘況。鑽石山龍蟠苑一名居屋買家，樓都未收，層樓已貶值63萬元或10%。<br />\n美聯物業何家豪表示，龍蟠苑D座10室其中兩個放盤(連地價)，同樣是中層，面積同為426方呎，只是樓上樓下(隔一層)。樓上單位今年5月放盤，由於開價達700萬元，故造就樓下單位於今年5月以663萬元賣出，呎價15,563元。但樓下賣出後，樓上單位卻不幸遇上淡市無人問津，即使上月減價至668萬元，「放咗成個月仍賣唔到」。直至昨晚，樓上單位突大幅落價，減至600萬元終賣出，呎價僅14,085元。代理形容，樓下買家真慘，層數低過人，卻買貴63萬元。土地註冊處資料顯示，該低層買家已簽正式買賣合約，料已支付樓價10%定金，但尚未完成交易，樓都未收層樓已貶值一成。<br />\n此外，龍蟠苑同類單位高峯期造價曾逼近700萬元，如A座高層14室，上月以685萬元連地價易手，呎價16,080元。<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180821/58591836\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F58591836&d=U1xicUYQoSLXF4XIAwMW3cmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e275037d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180821%2F58591836&h=96fe9396\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180821/58591836</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">居屋唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f27ca29986159be54a12b4d09a13181da5a329d5","tid":788511,"uid":51294,"like":45,"dislike":4,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"居屋係資助房屋市場 唔算數"},{"pid":"ea1079b388a25f74546689066e550cc3e6f084d9","tid":788511,"uid":106026,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"跌10%轉頭升返20%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <i